SELECT p.ProcessID, p.HCProcessId, p.ProcessName, p.GPM, p.GPO, p.RCOTower, p.RCOSubTower, p.ProcessControlEffectiveness, p.ProcessResidualRiskRating, p.ProcessCreationDate, p.DocumentUrl,
r.RAID, r.RALead, r.LastRADate, r.NextRADate, r.RAFrequency, r.RAStatus, '' AS O2CMapping, '' AS ProcessRollUp,
IF(((QUARTER(r.NextRADate)<=QUARTER(:currentDate)) AND (YEAR(r.NextRADate)<=YEAR(:currentDate))) OR (r.LastRADate is NULL) OR (STRCMP(p.ProcessResidualRiskRating, "Low")=0) OR (STRCMP(p.ProcessControlEffectiveness, "Low")=0), 1, 0) AS InScope,
(
  SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Process p JOIN RiskAssessment r ON r.ProcessID=p.ProcessID
  WHERE p.HCProcessId=IFNULL(:hcProcessId, p.HCProcessId) AND
  IF(:processID is NULL, true, p.ProcessID=:processID) AND
  IF(:processName is NULL, true, p.ProcessName=:processName) AND
  IF(:gpm is NULL, true, p.GPM=:gpm) AND
  IF(:gpo is NULL, true, p.GPO=:gpo) AND
  IF(:processResidualRiskRating is NULL, true, p.ProcessResidualRiskRating=:processResidualRiskRating) AND
  IF(:rcoTower is NULL, true, p.RCOTower=:rcoTower) AND
  IF(:rcoSubTower is NULL, true, p.RCOSubTower=:rcoSubTower) AND
  IF(:lastRADate is NULL, true, (QUARTER(r.LastRADate)=QUARTER(:lastRADate) AND YEAR(r.LastRADate)=YEAR(:lastRADate))) AND
  IF(:nextRADate is NULL, true, (QUARTER(r.NextRADate)=QUARTER(:nextRADate) AND YEAR(r.NextRADate)=YEAR(:nextRADate))) AND
  IF(:raLead is NULL, true, r.RALead=:raLead) AND
  IF(:inScope is NULL, true, :inScope=IF(((QUARTER(r.NextRADate)<=QUARTER(:currentDate)) AND (YEAR(r.NextRADate)<=YEAR(:currentDate))) OR (r.LastRADate is NULL) OR (STRCMP(p.ProcessResidualRiskRating, "Low")=0) OR (STRCMP(p.ProcessControlEffectiveness, "Low")=0), 1, 0))
) as RecordsCount
FROM Process p
JOIN RiskAssessment r
ON r.ProcessID=p.ProcessID
WHERE p.HCProcessId=IFNULL(:hcProcessId, p.HCProcessId) AND
IF(:processID is NULL, true, p.ProcessID=:processID) AND
IF(:processName is NULL, true, p.ProcessName=:processName) AND
IF(:gpm is NULL, true, p.GPM=:gpm) AND
IF(:gpo is NULL, true, p.GPO=:gpo) AND
IF(:processResidualRiskRating is NULL, true, p.ProcessResidualRiskRating=:processResidualRiskRating) AND
IF(:rcoTower is NULL, true, p.RCOTower=:rcoTower) AND
IF(:rcoSubTower is NULL, true, p.RCOSubTower=:rcoSubTower) AND
IF(:lastRADate is NULL, true, (QUARTER(r.LastRADate)=QUARTER(:lastRADate) AND YEAR(r.LastRADate)=YEAR(:lastRADate))) AND
IF(:nextRADate is NULL, true, (QUARTER(r.NextRADate)=QUARTER(:nextRADate) AND YEAR(r.NextRADate)=YEAR(:nextRADate))) AND
IF(:raLead is NULL, true, r.RALead=:raLead)
HAVING (:inScope is NULL OR :inScope=InScope)
ORDER BY CASE WHEN :nextRADateOrder = 'ASC'
              THEN r.NextRADate
              ELSE 0
              END ASC,
         CASE WHEN :nextRADateOrder = 'DESC'
              THEN r.NextRADate
              ELSE 0
              END DESC

SELECT p.ProcessID, p.HCProcessId, p.ProcessName, p.GPM, p.GPO, p.RCOTower, p.RCOSubTower, p.ProcessControlEffectiveness, p.ProcessResidualRiskRating, p.ProcessCreationDate, p.DocumentUrl,
r.RAID, r.RALead, r.LastRADate, r.NextRADate, r.RAFrequency, r.RAStatus, p.O2CMapping, p.ProcessRollUp, FALSE as InScope,
(
  SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Process p JOIN RiskAssessment r ON r.ProcessID=p.ProcessID
  WHERE r.RALead is not NULL AND p.GPO=:userEmail AND r.RAStatus=:raStatus AND r.RAStatus IN :statuses
) as RecordsCount
FROM Process p
JOIN RiskAssessment r
ON r.ProcessID=p.ProcessID
WHERE r.RALead is not NULL AND p.GPO=:userEmail AND r.RAStatus=:raStatus
ORDER BY CASE WHEN :order = 'ASC'
              THEN p.ProcessID
              ELSE 0
              END ASC,
         CASE WHEN :order = 'DESC'
              THEN p.ProcessID
              ELSE 0
              END DESC

SELECT p.ProcessID, p.HCProcessId, p.ProcessName, p.GPM, p.GPO, p.RCOTower, p.RCOSubTower, p.ProcessControlEffectiveness, p.ProcessResidualRiskRating, p.ProcessCreationDate, p.DocumentUrl,
r.RAID, r.RALead, r.LastRADate, r.NextRADate, r.RAFrequency, r.RAStatus, '' AS O2CMapping, '' AS ProcessRollUp, FALSE AS InScope,
(
  SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Process p JOIN RiskAssessment r ON r.ProcessID=p.ProcessID
  WHERE r.RALead=:userEmail AND r.RAStatus IN :statuses
) as RecordsCount
FROM Process p
JOIN RiskAssessment r
ON r.ProcessID=p.ProcessID
WHERE r.RALead=:userEmail AND r.RAStatus IN :statuses

SELECT p.ProcessID, p.HCProcessId, p.ProcessName, p.GPM, p.GPO, p.RCOTower, p.RCOSubTower, p.ProcessControlEffectiveness, p.ProcessResidualRiskRating, p.ProcessCreationDate, p.DocumentUrl,
r.RAID, r.RALead, r.LastRADate, r.NextRADate, r.RAFrequency, r.RAStatus, '' AS O2CMapping, '' AS ProcessRollUp, FALSE as InScope, 0 as RecordsCount

ON r.ProcessID=p.ProcessID

SELECT p.ProcessID, p.HCProcessId, p.ProcessName, p.GPM, p.GPO, p.RCOTower, p.RCOSubTower, p.ProcessControlEffectiveness, p.ProcessResidualRiskRating, p.ProcessCreationDate, p.DocumentUrl,
r.RAID, r.RALead, r.LastRADate, r.NextRADate, r.RAFrequency, r.RAStatus, p.O2CMapping, p.ProcessRollUp,
IF(((QUARTER(r.NextRADate)<=QUARTER(:currentDate)) AND (YEAR(r.NextRADate)<=YEAR(:currentDate))) OR (r.LastRADate is NULL) OR (STRCMP(p.ProcessResidualRiskRating, "Low")=0) OR (STRCMP(p.ProcessControlEffectiveness, "Low")=0), 1, 0) AS InScope,
(
  SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Process p JOIN RiskAssessment r ON r.ProcessID=p.ProcessID
  WHERE IF(:processID is NULL, true, p.ProcessID=:processID) AND
  IF(:gpm is NULL, true, p.GPM=:gpm) AND
  IF(:gpo is NULL, true, p.GPO=:gpo) AND
  IF(:rcoTower is NULL, true, p.RCOTower=:rcoTower) AND
  IF(:inScope is NULL, true, :inScope=IF(((QUARTER(r.NextRADate)<=QUARTER(:currentDate)) AND (YEAR(r.NextRADate)<=YEAR(:currentDate))) OR (r.LastRADate is NULL) OR (STRCMP(p.ProcessResidualRiskRating, "Low")=0) OR (STRCMP(p.ProcessControlEffectiveness, "Low")=0), 1, 0))
) as RecordsCount
FROM Process p
JOIN RiskAssessment r
ON r.ProcessID=p.ProcessID
WHERE IF(:processID is NULL, true, p.ProcessID=:processID) AND
IF(:gpm is NULL, true, p.GPM=:gpm) AND
IF(:gpo is NULL, true, p.GPO=:gpo) AND
IF(:rcoTower is NULL, true, p.RCOTower=:rcoTower)
HAVING (:inScope is NULL OR :inScope=InScope)
